Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.20,0:00:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.08,0:00:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.94,0:00:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out, Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me at him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you save Mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.66,0:00:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.74,0:00:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata was busy saving Zessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.63,0:00:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.94,0:00:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's not the time for arguing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.96,0:00:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Focus on getting Mix back!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.63,0:00:38.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get her back?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.60,0:00:41.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I'd be here if I knew how to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.80,0:00:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.05,0:00:52.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After the Gate closed, we couldn't \Ndetect any trace of spatial distortion.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.16,0:00:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then how do we save Mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.57,0:00:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the High Commander when we need him?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.36,0:01:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees something.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.39,0:01:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fate of our two worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and where to find the seed of destiny that can change it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.98,0:01:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ants...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.35,0:01:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and their antsy antics.{ari, ariari to ari no mama ni (ants, behaving simply as ants do)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.35,0:02:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Why did it have to turn out like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.18,0:03:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}I never got to hold you in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.77,0:03:09.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never got to take those big bangs and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.44,0:03:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm such an idiot! I should die! Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.39,0:03:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you eat, Andy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.65,0:03:38.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's sent back yesterday's, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.54,0:03:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What else can I do for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.17,0:03:44.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've lost someone special. I don't want Andy to go through the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:53.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.32,0:03:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.48,0:04:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope Mix is all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.77,0:04:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about Zessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.15,0:04:14.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking another day off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.25,0:04:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really broken up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.61,0:04:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so pathetic. I'm an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.89,0:04:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you save me, Amata?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you won't choose me, so all there is for me here is pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:51.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That vision again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.96,0:04:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the... what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't cry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.15,0:05:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're the same, you and I. The unchosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.66,0:05:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, the unchosen, must know how it feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.14,0:05:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To carelessly take the offered hand, only for it to be snatched away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.06,0:05:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can rip off that hand and give it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you what you desire. I will open the Dimension Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:48.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I want a promise from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:13.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.11,0:06:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you going by yourself to search for the High Commander?{pro exposition}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really understand myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.70,0:06:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.39,0:06:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikono Suzushiro, your power is to connect those who are so divided once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.57,0:06:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You connect all the fragmented souls together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.28,0:06:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you're the one who said now's the time for everyone to work together. {timing check}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Connecting people together is my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.42,0:06:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's got...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...nothing to do with this? Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't just sit and be useless while we lose Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.00,0:07:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:03.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're needed here if Altair attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the only one without a combat Element power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.38,0:07:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.50,0:07:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I've had to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.10,0:07:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't all this time because I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.62,0:07:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when I come back...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I come back, I'll say it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.00,0:07:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.02,0:07:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't give Amata a break, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.10,0:07:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems to like that boy, Kagura,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.69,0:07:49.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it growls at the rest of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.42,0:07:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think it doesn't like me or Amata?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.53,0:07:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.47,0:07:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.50,0:08:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I get to like anyone, it growls at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.63,0:08:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you do like Amata, Mikono!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.58,0:08:20.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't want to get hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.48,0:08:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that hurt Amata and Zessica.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:27.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to tell him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.47,0:08:31.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First I have to connect everybody and save Mix.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.31,0:08:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Dimension Gate has opened above the academy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.41,0:08:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they've finally come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.35,0:08:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.28,0:08:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.92,0:09:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've not detected any enemy machines!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.44,0:09:02.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a Gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.98,0:09:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can go to Altair and take Mix back!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.59,0:09:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool it! This could be a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.24,0:09:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.50,0:09:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Donar is completely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.91,0:09:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The enemy is inviting us in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.74,0:09:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will give you what you desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.84,0:09:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Fudo gone, we can't send Aquarion, our main force, to Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.90,0:09:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're just going to abandon Mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.32,0:09:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand how you feel, Andy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.56,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we can't do anything for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.45,0:09:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.74,0:09:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander! I mean, Principal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.60,0:09:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chairman Crea, this is for you from High Commander Fudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.94,0:10:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A donut?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eek! Ants!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.15,0:10:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.50,0:10:12.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.14,0:10:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be a message from Fudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.70,0:10:25.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perhaps he is telling us, "Don't hesitate! Leap into the ring!"
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.03,0:10:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Into the ring?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.69,0:10:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Else you will never get the sweet within."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweet... that's Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Orders from the High Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.18,0:10:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Deploy Aquarion at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:44.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:48.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For you, all for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I granted your desire and opened the gate for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girl with hair the color of grass,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.95,0:10:59.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will fulfill your promise in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.13,0:11:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then your turn will come, Kagura.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.74,0:11:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Vector Y, all green.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.14,0:11:14.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready to deploy any time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.98,0:11:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm deeply sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.85,0:11:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I will have this seat, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cayenne?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then who's in the Vector?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.76,0:11:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade Elan deploying!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.71,0:11:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrade!? {missing line}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.73,0:11:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must reach the unknown world and hear its sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.43,0:11:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to perfect my final melody.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.90,0:11:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do a coed Union yet. No, I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.18,0:11:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saving my first time for you, Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Infiltration Union! Go, Aquarion!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.15,0:12:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aquarion Evol!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.18,0:12:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will take time for that soldier's mind to stabilize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.35,0:12:31.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the final steps are already complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.33,0:12:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And those piloting talents are extraordinary.{I never thought I'd be the sort of writer who has to dance around pronouns}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.65,0:12:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may not be the result I was hoping for,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but now that we've lost Jin, we could use an extra fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Izumo, the Dimensional Gate has opened!{what did we do with sama again?}{"Master" but "Sir" sounds better now}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:47.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Did Mikage make another move?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes an enormous amount of \Nenergy to open the Dimension Road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.50,0:12:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Each activation drains the precious little energy left to Altair.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:01.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikage knows that, and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.80,0:13:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something came over! Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.56,0:13:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We... we can't detect them, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.96,0:13:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No mass or heat readings at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.39,0:13:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there an error in the Gate?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.45,0:13:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little longer, Yunoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.65,0:13:30.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Altair?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.42,0:13:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.30,0:13:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole surface is covered with metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we can get in from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are those graves? There are so many...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.51,0:14:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.20,0:14:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can only keep them transparent for half a day at best.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.74,0:14:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have to find Mix quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound of this world is an old woman's rasping wail of grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.66,0:14:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slow down, Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:37.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on, Mix! I'm coming to save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.97,0:14:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yunoha, you should have stayed with the Vectors.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.30,0:14:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.70,0:14:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to see Jin's world with Tama.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.18,0:15:02.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Alicia? That's the Skies of Aquaria!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are they showing a movie from Earth on Altair?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.60,0:15:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.94,0:15:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jin's device had an image of Alicia in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.85,0:15:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom... you're somewhere on this planet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.82,0:15:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's an iVision{did he actually just say ai-bijon} of Alicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.65,0:15:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't see that every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.89,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's the matter with you? You look funny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.10,0:15:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get away, Yunoha!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.71,0:15:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost look like Iguras.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.16,0:15:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are these bags?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:45.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zessica!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.95,0:15:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Creep.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our Element Suits will attract unwanted attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.76,0:15:53.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had best find a change.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.40,0:16:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This place stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.09,0:16:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just keep going, Andy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.49,0:16:12.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something else weird about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:21.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears this city is populated only by men.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.27,0:16:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or perhaps this entire planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you think that's why they're kidnapping girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.05,0:16:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right, Zessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.58,0:16:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My throat's been feeling weird since we got on this planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.96,0:16:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, mine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.15,0:16:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's something in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.36,0:16:43.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can feel it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That building over there...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.04,0:16:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.70,0:16:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to the data Jin left for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that's the enemy's command center.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.44,0:16:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? We don't know if Mix is in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.00,0:17:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's go and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.06,0:17:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.05,0:17:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.52,0:17:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy's hole digging power is definitely stronger now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.80,0:17:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Intruders detected in the hangar block!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:22.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All units, phase one battle stations!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have reports that they are infiltrators from Vega!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.30,0:17:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must assume they have Gnis!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.25,0:17:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your training may not have prepared you for this type of combat,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so stay hidden and stay alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move a muscle!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I said don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.04,0:17:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Holes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.97,0:17:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.10,0:17:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know if I can control myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, you're going to be our guide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.20,0:17:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do as I say, or...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.99,0:17:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put a hole in your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.72,0:18:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.38,0:18:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.41,0:18:17.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, Amata! We'll hold them off here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:19.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two search for Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.71,0:18:24.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful, Amata. Don't get into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.35,0:18:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.32,0:18:29.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.23,0:18:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A crude, ugly dissonance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will not allow you to interrupt the melody of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Contrary Twister!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.23,0:19:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.12,0:19:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good. Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That wound...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you found them yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.90,0:19:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.60,0:19:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Go search area 83!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.60,0:19:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you treat my wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.98,0:19:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut it. I don't want them tracking us by your blood trail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.15,0:19:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:19:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a dead end!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This elevator is the only way up the tower.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.90,0:20:04.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then open the lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, we just want to save our friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.97,0:20:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll do anything to save that friend, understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.00,0:20:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.79,0:20:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure why, but you can't kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.75,0:20:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amata, get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.87,0:20:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.79,0:21:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we both get caught, there won't be anyone left to save Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.75,0:21:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got this! I'm the immortal Andy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.27,0:21:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Andy...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.58,0:21:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.43,0:21:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The suspected Vega infiltrator is headed into the upper block!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.08,0:21:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The boy with wings!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.42,0:21:43.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Skies of Aquaria?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:21:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.40,0:22:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.82,0:22:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me go! Give me back my Mix!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.24,0:22:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{hate this ed}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.59,0:24:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mix, I want you to fill my holes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.53,0:24:15.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My nostrils long to smell you,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's a bad feeling in my pores,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.11,0:24:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you've left a gaping hole in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{this title: First Reunion}
